                        <div class="border card bg-light">
                            <img src="icons/coll (5).jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h4 class="card-title">VILLA MAR Y PALMA</h4>
                                <p class="card-text">Villa Mar y Palma is a splendid and elegant vacation home with a privileged oceanfront view, and enjoys a prime location, strategically situated in front of the renowned Teeth of the Dog golf course. Here, peace, charm and nature converge magnificently. The quality furnishings, delicate decoration and attention to detail combine to create a delirious paradise that creates a calming ambiance for each and every visitor.</p>
