                                <h4 class="card-title">CASA GLORIA</h4>
                                <p class="card-text">Located near the world-famous Teeth of the Dog golf course and the Caribbean Sea, this luxurious villa, designed by the best architectural team in CASA DE CAMPO®, is already breaking records in elegance and charm. The house faces a very long, elegant pool and gazebo, both framing awe-inspiring views from every angle. It also features a modern art collection and a state-of-the-art kitchen.</p>
